### Variables
@host = 127.0.0.1:8016
@baseUrl = http://{{host}}

### Get all sites
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sites

### Search sites by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sites?name=toto

### Search sites by geographic bounds (rectangle)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sites?minLat=48.0&maxLat=49.0&minLon=2.0&maxLon=3.0

### Search sites in Europe (approximate bounds)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sites?minLat=35.0&maxLat=70.0&minLon=-10.0&maxLon=40.0

### Search sites with multiple criteria (name + geographic bounds)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sites?name=ch√¢teau&minLat=45.0&maxLat=50.0&minLon=0.0&maxLon=8.0

### Get specific site by ID (using id_number from XML data)
